  <brief_title>An Extension Study of Entacapone in Patients With Parkinson's Disease With End-of-dose Wearing-off. This Study is Not Recruiting in the United States</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Extension Study to Phase IIb Dose-finding Study of Entacapone in Patients With Parkinson's Disease With End-of-dose Wearing-off</official_title>
  <sponsors>
