  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of the long-term treatment
      of entacapone in patients with Parkinson's disease with end-of-dose wearing-off.

      This study is not recruiting patients in the United States.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
